  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improving the rural education in Guachene-Colombia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Lady, a teenager from Guachene (Colombia) like many others in rural Colombia is at risk of dropping out of her studies because their school does not offer them adequate conditions to want to go to study. The Escala program has arrived at one of the rural schools in Guachene to help Lady and her classmate graduate and have a better future. At Escala, we are convinced that a person who stays in school and finishes the learning process until graduation will have a better quality of life.</narrative>
  </description>
